Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝者，愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妮娜，恭喜妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們二位就是代表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的畢業紀念舞鬥\N同時是風華宮落成典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有許多來賓前來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好注意\N別侮辱了加爾德羅貝之名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴·瑪格麗特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是她們兩位的候補
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為輸了就疏於鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，這是當然，瑪莉亞女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔，我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，螞蟻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之妳做得很好，妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，代表戰是二對二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到今後要跟愛莉卡\N搭檔練習，我頭就痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好妳跟她\N可以成為好拍檔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，千萬別忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳註定要成為阿爾泰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪殿下的乙HiME一事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，父親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彼此重疊的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖進記憶深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨而下的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我訴說著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護」的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度仰望 無限寬闊的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了 那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱切地 強烈地 勇猛地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在沒有光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能感覺到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第16話 這是約定喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也到了這個時期了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是“考驗”儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週是畢業舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister任命典禮等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有許多活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有升級考試等著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了回應真祖之心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，我幫妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等等會帶東西過去給妳們吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待妳來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很賣力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟對手是第一名的千繪姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有第二名的詩帆姊姊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個每天都練習到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，我是說妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅每天帶東西給她們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還替她們\N做掃除一類的工作不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也只能幫這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，只要看著她們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有種我也要加油的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，有需要要講喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，依琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那兩位很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪姊姊對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個學妹真是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是什麼好姊姊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很優秀，很好帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至認真覺得我太疏忽妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，巴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我自認還是有關心妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很在意妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊姊會難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道\N是妳叫美也做出那些事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂妳在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，一直以來都很謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯也為我們打氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，可以再加長練習時間了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛剛是不是想講什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，那是我的份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先來的先贏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你跟骯髒的黑團有掛勾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前不是也聯手過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼分裂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得遺憾\N不過還是放棄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道我們會拒絕，還故意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能默默旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要出動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻意到火堆裡撿栗子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓人民們再等下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五柱之試也已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年份的珊瑚與珍珠GEM\N生產也很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，退學的美也同學的GEM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經讓羊水分解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正準備送去重新結晶化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留那邊如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是追不上史密斯的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業典禮也快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括那個新型奴獸的事情\N要重新檢討一下對應方針
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正，雖然持續緊張狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過目前並沒有什麼大動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡快竣工了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王似乎也恢復幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果照這樣努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚可以收回民心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能這樣持續下去\N都不出事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，現在開始舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由真祖主持的五柱之試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大新聞大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊被選上五柱了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空缺的第四柱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後佛羅倫斯的查理國王\N向詩帆姊姊提出乙HiME邀請呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔，卡迪亞退讓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟有茜姊姊和和也先生那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為過去對立國家的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲劇性喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是外交上一張有效的王牌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽說受到很熱烈的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊似乎很滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人幸福的話就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪姊姊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要回到出身國愛瑞斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說好像是要當\N阿米特吉准將的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊們真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個個都找到出路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有還有，聽說靜留姊姊回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓靜留姊姊看到妳的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，我們這些該準備考試的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是乖乖唸書去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分子生物學我有不懂的地方耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得把這個還給陽子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去還吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有事情要請教老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳被選上五柱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不值得恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不過，不是很了不起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生計劃都被打亂了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我加入老處女軍團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管妳是真祖還是誰咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊，保重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯汀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有看到依琳娜同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情要問她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，依琳娜是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許在圖書館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問，發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個液體很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不小心碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會出大事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有事要請教老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那樣挺不錯的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是埃爾斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等食物等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點，埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好，愛莉卡妳們沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是無法知道\N為什麼會發生那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之埃爾斯的傷勢不嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令大家安心下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子老師說如果直接\N接觸到那個可是很不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去散一下步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好有及時治療
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也多虧有奈米機械\N在升級考試前就能痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過奈米機械真的很了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從之前就覺得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不光是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能注射就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學的神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（站在內心的窗邊）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（命運的側臉）\N這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（點亮守護夢想之光吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（星兒只是孤單地）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（宣告選擇）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（心愛的人兒啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（呼喚我就能改變）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（等待覺醒國度的）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（古早古早的故事）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（奉獻出在這心中）\N妳們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們分別知道\N同一首歌的不同歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這就像受到命運的結合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有這種感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好冷淡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣講嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要給那個叔叔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼字錯了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有人怪異到要補助妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想邀請他來\N觀看畢業紀念舞鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要是我受傷就泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也謝謝妳，埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會，我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有妳們兩位在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會也想加把勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個人一定\N都要成為Meister-乙HiME喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們就不發一語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠交到這麼棒的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是叔叔的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，一起寄過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我綉的手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力縫製出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在畢業舞鬥的時候\N揮舞這條手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一定可以找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要一句話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我親自向你道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給親愛的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過天氣真的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠迎接今天就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…靜留也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有點遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年幾乎所有國家都不是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是派代表前來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟現況如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒差
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們擔心的因素也會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去從沒有\N珊瑚打贏珍珠的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作是測驗自己的本領\N放輕鬆去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了父親…我一定會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，螞蟻仔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受邀而來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們請我務必來欣賞舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可別給妮娜扯後腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會成為Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了來看我的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的那個叔叔，一定會看著妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待各位展現一場\N符合畢業紀念的舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位盡全力發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟那座城堡一起重生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，別忘了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是假契約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妳可是第一個\N跟我訂契約的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行加爾德羅貝\N畢業紀念舞鬥比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穩住點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是將過去累積的捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅捲捲黃捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得隨便怎樣都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之臣民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以舞鬥為開場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為各位揭開\N我的城一風華宮的新面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的治世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與這座城同樣由此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…跟真白的圖完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪嗜好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個機關是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是更…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.73,0:22:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:22:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情不得了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後會變成怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蒼之舞／思念，飄散之時）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂
